(2, 1, 'introduction_letter', 'TP Introduction Letter', 'Request for Student Placement Letter for Federal University of Kashere - NUC Bachelor\'s Degree requirements', '<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>{today}</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>The Principal/Head Teacher,</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>_____________________________________________</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>_____________________________________________</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>Sir/Madam,</span></span></p><h3 style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span><strong>REQUEST FOR PLACEMENT OF STUDENT FOR THE {current_session} TEACHING PRACTICE EXERCISE</strong></span></span></h3><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>I am writing to request your kind consideration in offering a place of attachment for the <strong>{current_session}</strong> Student Teaching Practice exercise. The bearer of this letter, Mr./Mrs./Miss <strong>{student_name}</strong> with Registration Number <strong>{student_regno}</strong> is a student at our esteemed institution, majoring in <strong>{student_program}</strong>, and is required to undertake a Teaching Practice exercise as part of the requirements set by the National Universities Commission (NUC) for the award of a Bachelor\'s Degree in Education.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>We would be grateful if your school could accommodate the student for this critical component of their academic training. We also kindly request that you monitor and guide the student to support his/her professional growth and development.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>We are confident that our student will adhere to all rules and regulations of your school. However, any instances of misconduct on the part of the student should be reported to the University so that appropriate action can be taken.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>We therefore, request you to please confirm his/her acceptance by signing on the attached form.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>Thank you for your usual cooperation.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span></span></span><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"168\" height=\"42\" style=\"width: 168px; height: 42px;\"></p><p style=\"line-height: 0.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>{coordinator_name}</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 0.5;\"><strong>Teaching Practice Coordinator</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 0.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>{coordinator_phone}</span></span></p>', '.hr-line { border-top: 2px solid #000; margin-bottom: 20px; }\r\n.fs { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }\r\n.float-right { float: right; }\r\n.text-center { text-align: center; }\r\n.text-l { font-size: 14px; }\r\n.fw-bold { font-weight: bold; }\r\n.letter-subject { font-size: 16px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 20px 0; }\r\n.signature-area { margin-top: 40px; }\r\n.signature-area img { height: 60px; }\r\np { margin-bottom: 15px; }', NULL, NULL, 'A4', 'portrait', NULL, 'published', 43, '2025-12-31 17:01:06', 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 2, '2025-12-30 13:21:11', '2025-12-31 17:01:06');
