(3, 1, 'posting_letter', 'TP Posting Letter', 'Official Posting Letter for students to take to their teaching practice school', '<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>{posting_date}</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>The Principal,<br>{school_name}.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>Sir,</span></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>POSTING LETTER FOR {current_session} TEACHING PRACTICE EXERCISE</span></span></h2><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>This letter serves to formally introduce <strong>{student_name}</strong> (Registration No.: <strong>{student_regno}</strong>), a student-teacher from our institution, who has been assigned to undertake the mandatory Teaching Practice exercise at your esteemed school. The exercise is pre-requisite of the award of Bachelor\'s Degree in Education, and we sincerely appreciate your cooperation in facilitating this pedagogical training.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>The exercise shall span a period of {tp_duration}, commencing on <strong>{tp_start_date}</strong> and concluding on <strong>{tp_end_date}</strong>. In accordance with the revised curriculum, the assessment of the student-teacher will be conducted jointly by the University and your school. The assessment forms have been provided for your use. We kindly request that evaluations be completed every three (3) weeks and submitted to our visiting supervisors for institutional assessment. All assessments shall be treated with strict confidentiality.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>We recommend that the student-teacher be actively engaged in both academic and extracurricular activities, including but not limited to classroom instruction, pastoral duties, and ancillary school functions. This comprehensive exposure is designed to enhance their professional development.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>The University deeply values and appreciate your continued partnership in our collective mission to nurture competent educators for the academic community.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>Thank you.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span></span></span><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"168\" height=\"42\" style=\"width: 168px; height: 42px;\"></p><p style=\"line-height: 0.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span>{coordinator_name}</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 0.5;\"><strong>Teaching Practice Coordinator</strong></p>', '.hr-line { border-top: 2px solid #000; margin-bottom: 20px; }\r\n.fs { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }\r\n.float-right { float: right; }\r\n.text-center { text-align: center; }\r\n.text-l { font-size: 14px; }\r\n.fw-bold { font-weight: bold; }\r\n.mt-2 { margin-top: 10px; }\r\n.signature-area { margin-top: 40px; }\r\n.signature-area img { height: 70px; }\r\np { margin-bottom: 15px; }', NULL, NULL, 'A4', 'portrait', NULL, 'published', 11, '2025-12-30 13:21:11', 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 2, '2025-12-30 13:21:11', '2026-01-20 17:48:36');
